# TASK_PACKET
ID: CRUSHR-FORMAT-09
Title: Metadata survivability and necessity audit
Role: BUILDER
Phase: Format research
Depends-On: CRUSHR-FORMAT-08

## Objective

FORMAT-08 demonstrated that metadata placement strategies produced
no measurable difference because metadata layers never survived the
existing corruption scenarios.

FORMAT-09 expands the corruption harness to explicitly test
metadata survivability and determine whether metadata layers
actually contribute to recovery outcomes.

This packet does NOT change the archive format.

It expands the corruption grid used by the lab harness.

